author: @DevG-rp8uf
text: Nice concept.....but it's good to remember that following fate is sensible only for those with good luck at that moment. Several had fate pull them in negative direction by having situations arranged thus. When everything came together for something wrong to happen,sometimes you have the choice to say yes or no to it. If you keep silent and go along with whatever is happening, however the current flows, good or bad, will come to you. Its better to use one's intelligence in all circumstances and consider if something is good for one, thinking of every aspect. Trusting fate is not always sensible. Even God might only be able to speak through a person who gives soft suggestion. Once a step is taken, perhaps nothing can help. So using one's own intelligence, would be more sensible than blindly following fate. All the best girlsâ¤
